the martial arts kid is a 2015 martial arts film directed by michael baumgarten and starring don ' the dragon ' wilson and cynthia rothrock as a couple who take in their nephew jansen panettiere , and teach him martial arts when he is bullied .   the film has been given major rave for its anti-bullying message .   most of the supporting cast of the film are actual martial artists , some of whom appear as themselves in the film .